# Bönetider map tiles — optional. With no key set, the map uses OpenFreeMap
# (planet vector tiles + low-zoom Natural Earth shaded relief). With a
# MapTiler key set, the same OpenMapTiles vector schema is served by MapTiler
# AND a high-zoom hillshade (z12) is enabled so the Scandinavian relief carries
# all the way to city zoom instead of fading by z9.
#
# Free tier: 100k tile requests / month. Sign up at https://www.maptiler.com/
# then paste the key here (no quotes, no spaces).
#
# EXPO_PUBLIC_* vars are inlined into the JS bundle at build/OTA time. For local
# `pnpm android` development, this .env is read automatically. For preview OTA
# updates, set the same var on EAS:
#   eas env:create EXPO_PUBLIC_MAPTILER_KEY=… --environment preview --visibility plaintext
#
# EXPO_PUBLIC_MAPTILER_KEY=
